# My Pets Feature

## Overview
The My Pets section is the core private functionality where users create digital profiles for their pets and record their growth journey through a timeline.

## Screen Structure

### PetsScreen (Main)
- **Location**: `lib/features/pets/pets_screen.dart`
- **Components**:
  - Header with "My Pets" title and "+" button
  - Horizontal scrolling pet avatar selector
  - Pet profile card (info, birthday, gotcha day)
  - Reminders section
  - Growth Track timeline
  - Archive button at bottom

### AddPetScreen
- **Location**: `lib/features/pets/add_pet_screen.dart`
- **Form Fields**:
  - Pet name (required)
  - Species (dropdown: Dog, Cat, Hamster, etc.)
  - Breed (text input)
  - Gender (radio: Male, Female)
  - Birthday (date picker)
  - Gotcha Day (date picker)
  - Hobbies (multiline text)
  - Avatar URL (text input for demo)

### AddReminderScreen
- **Location**: `lib/features/pets/add_reminder_screen.dart`
- **Form Fields**:
  - Title (required)
  - Description
  - Due date (date picker)
  - Type (dropdown: ReminderType enum)

### AddGrowthTrackScreen
- **Location**: `lib/features/pets/add_growth_track_screen.dart`
- **Form Fields**:
  - Title (required)
  - Description (multiline)
  - Date (date picker)
  - Image URLs (text input, comma-separated for demo)

