## Date Calculations

### Age Calculation
```dart
String calculateAge(DateTime birthday) {
  final now = DateTime.now();
  final difference = now.difference(birthday);
  final years = difference.inDays ~/ 365;
  final months = (difference.inDays % 365) ~/ 30;
  
  if (years > 0) {
    return '$years year${years > 1 ? 's' : ''} old';
  } else {
    return '$months month${months > 1 ? 's' : ''} old';
  }
}
```

### Days Until Reminder
```dart
String daysUntilDue(DateTime dueDate) {
  final now = DateTime.now();
  final difference = dueDate.difference(now).inDays;
  
  if (difference < 0) return 'Overdue';
  if (difference == 0) return 'Today';
  if (difference == 1) return 'Tomorrow';
  return 'In $difference days';
}
```

## Automatic Reminders
When a pet is added, automatically create:
1. Birthday reminder (annual, on birthday)
2. Gotcha Day reminder (annual, on gotcha day)

## Archive Functionality
- Show confirmation dialog
- Set `pet.isActive = false`
- Keep all data (reminders, growth tracks)
- Show archived pets in a separate section (optional)
- Archived pets are read-only
